omain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=eiqLDwAAQBAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"SAMPLE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"Here are tales that will make readers laugh and cry and embrace with passion the calling of our better angels to change the way we take care of ourselves, our families, our communities, and the world.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"Our Better Angels\", \"authors\": [\"Jonathan Reckford\"], \"infoLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=eiqLDwAAQBAJ&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"Seven Simple Virtues That Will Change Your Life and the World\", \"pageCount\": 256, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"St. Martin\'s Essentials\", \"categories\": [\"Self-Help\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=eiqLDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=eiqLDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"Inspiring and insightful, Our Better Angels: Seven Simple Virtues That Will Change Your Life and the World celebrates the shared principles that unite and enable us to overcome life’s challenges together. “When the waters rise, so do our better angels.”—President Jimmy Carter Jonathan Reckford, the CEO of Habitat for Humanity, has seen time and again the powerful benefits that arise when people from all walks of life work together to help one another. In this uplifting book, he shares true stories of people involved with Habitat as volunteers and future homeowners who embody seven timeless virtues—kindness, community, empowerment, joy, respect, generosity, and service—and shows how we can all practice these to improve the quality of our own lives as well as those around us. A Vietnam veteran finds peace where he was once engaged in war. An impoverished single mother offers her family’s time and energy to enrich their neighbors’ lives. A Zambian family of nine living in a makeshift tent makes room to shelter even more. A teenager grieving for his mother honors her love and memory by ensuring other people have a place to call home. A former president of the United States leads by example with a determined work ethic that motivates everyone around him to be the best version of themselves. These stories, and many others, illustrate how virtues become values, how cooperation becomes connection, and how even the smallest act of compassion can encourage actions that transform the world around us. Here are tales that will make readers laugh and cry and embrace with passion the calling of our better angels to change the way we take care of ourselves, our families, our communities, and the world.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=eiqLDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=angels&hl=&cd=7&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": true, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"2019-10-08\", \"contentVersion\": \"1.4.4.0.preview.2\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=eiqLDwAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781250239259\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1250239257\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"n0KKDQAAQBAJ\", \"etag\": \"fE6S0NmrUNM\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/n0KKDQAAQBAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"PARTIAL\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=n0KKDQAAQBAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"SAMPLE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"With great feeling, Burnham offers an eloquent report from the place where earth and heaven meet. A wondrous journey into the world of angels, this book is a song of praise to life.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"A Book of Angels\", \"authors\": [\"Sophy Burnham\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=n0KKDQAAQBAJ&dq=angels&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"Reflections on Angels Past and Present, and True Stories of How They Touch Our L ives\", \"pageCount\": 384, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"Penguin\", \"categories\": [\"Body, Mind & Spirit\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=n0KKDQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=n0KKDQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"A gorgeous new edition of the New York Times bestseller that has sold more than a million copies. \\\"A golden conjunction of heaven and earth...reminding us that there are angels in every religion.\\\" -The Washington Post \\\"As far as angels are concerned, now you see them, now you don\'t. A Book of Angels gives us a lovely, sustained glimpse.\\\" -Chicago Tribune When Sophy Burnham wrote A Book of Angels, she inspired a phenomenon. An instant bestseller when it was originally published in 1990, this beautiful book not only tells the extraordinary true stories of present-day encounters with angels, but also traces the study of angels throughout history and in different cultures. Burnham writes about the powerful male angels, Buddhist bodhisattvas, Islamic angels, Hindu Apsaras, the mysterious angels of the Jewish Kabbalah, cherubim, seraphim, guardian angels, the angel of death, and others. What are angels? What do they look like? Whom do they choose to visit? Why do they appear sometimes and not others, and would you recognize one if it appeared before you? With great feeling, Burnham offers an eloquent report from the place where earth and heaven meet. A wondrous journey into the world of angels, this book is a song of praise to life.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=n0KKDQAAQBAJ&pg=PP1&dq=angels&hl=&cd=8&source=gbs_api\", \"ratingsCount\": 3, \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"averageRating\": 2, \"publishedDate\": \"2011-03-31\", \"contentVersion\": \"0.1.0.0.preview.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/A_Book_of_Angels.html?hl=&id=n0KKDQAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781585428779\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1585428779\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"-E8xDwAAQBAJ\", \"etag\": \"TAmU8BeCM8k\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/-E8xDwAAQBAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"PARTIAL\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=-E8xDwAAQBAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"SAMPLE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"In this volume renowned scholar Loren Stuckenbruck explores aspects of that influence and demonstrates how the myth was reused and adapted to address new religious and cultural contexts.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"The Myth of Rebellious Angels\", \"authors\": [\"Stuckenbruck, Loren T.\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=-E8xDwAAQBAJ&dq=angels&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"\", \"pageCount\": 427, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"Wm. B. Eerdmans Publishing\", \"categories\": [\"Religion\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=-E8xDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=-E8xDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"The mythical story of fallen angels preserved in 1 Enoch and related literature was profoundly influential during the Second Temple period. In this volume renowned scholar Loren Stuckenbruck explores aspects of that influence and demonstrates how the myth was reused and adapted to address new religious and cultural contexts. Stuckenbruck considers a variety of themes, including demonology, giants, exorcism, petitionary prayer, the birth and activity of Jesus, the Holy Spirit, the conversion of Gentiles, \\\"apocalyptic\\\" and the understanding of time, and more. He also offers a theological framework for the myth of fallen angels through which to reconsider several New Testament texts--the Synoptic Gospels, the Gospel of John, Acts, Paul\'s letters, and the book of Revelation.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=-E8xDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=angels&hl=&cd=9&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": true}, \"publishedDate\": \"2017-02-17\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/The_Myth_of_Rebellious_Angels.html?hl=&id=-E8xDwAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9780802873156\"}