. The result is a study which will be of interest to students and scholars working in the digital humanities, corpus linguistics, and discourse studies.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=1ZqgDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA17&dq=big&hl=&cd=9&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": true, \"image\": true}, \"publishedDate\": \"2019-07-03\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=1ZqgDwAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9783030167882\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"3030167887\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"Q1auDwAAQBAJ\", \"etag\": \"3P44S6CyNRQ\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"offers\": [{\"giftable\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 46950000}, \"retailPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 37090000}, \"finskyOfferType\": 1}], \"buyLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=Q1auDwAAQBAJ&rdid=book-Q1auDwAAQBAJ&rdot=1&source=gbs_api\", \"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"amount\": 46.95, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"retailPrice\": {\"amount\": 37.09, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"saleability\": \"FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/Q1auDwAAQBAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": true, \"acsTokenLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/Big_Data-sample-pdf.acsm?id=Q1auDwAAQBAJ&format=pdf&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api\"}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": true, \"acsTokenLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/Big_Data-sample-epub.acsm?id=Q1auDwAAQBAJ&format=epub&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api\"}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"PARTIAL\", \"