cription\": \"In Demons, Nephilim, and Angels, Etienne explains how Satan, his demons, fallen angels, aliens, and the giant Nephilim originated and have infiltrated the original earth, the chaotic earth, the restored earth, and the world that we live in. The original earth was a spiritual world that included Lucifer, the angels, cherubs, seraphim, and other created beings and heaven. God created Lucifer and the angels to serve Him. Lucifer was determined to exercise his will to sit on God\'s throne. He wanted to be God and not a servant of God. Lucifer was a hybrid being, half-man and half-angel. He was the cause of the chaotic earth. In the chaotic earth, God was angry with Lucifer for trying to take His place and tampering with the genes/DNA of the other creatures that lived on the earth and the planets at that time. God destroyed the earth and Rahab, where Lucifer was king, with a flood and turned it upside down and in darkness. Lucifer was kicked out of heaven and demoted to the prince of the power of the air. After God restored the earth and recreated it, He made mankind in His image. Lucifer detests mankind and wants to alter our DNA.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=4-VZAwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=demons&hl=&cd=7&source=gbs_api\", \"ratingsCount\": 2, \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": true}, \"averageRating\": 4.5, \"publishedDate\": \"2014-04\", \"contentVersion\": \"0.1.0.0.preview.1\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": true, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/Demons_Nephilim_Angels.html?hl=&id=4-VZAwAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781490731735\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1490731733\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"ya3Nq-_dqG8C\", \"etag\": \"BLhaZ0AYRQo\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbo