th Africa and later against whites in India. The author also finds evidence of multiple cover-ups designed to hide Gandhi\'s real history, including even collusion to cover up the murder of an American.This provocative thesis is sure to be controversial.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=gJxzUWIecSYC&pg=PA1&dq=ghandi&hl=&cd=4&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"contentVersion\": \"0.5.0.0.preview.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/Gandhi.html?hl=&id=gJxzUWIecSYC\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781615923601\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1615923608\"}]}}, {\"id\": \"FauJL7LKXmkC\", \"etag\": \"6DFk2wvs5Z8\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/FauJL7LKXmkC\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": true, \"acsTokenLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/Gandhi-sample-epub.acsm?id=FauJL7LKXmkC&format=epub&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api\"}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"PARTIAL\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=FauJL7LKXmkC&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"SAMPLE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"The author, the grandson of Mohandas Gandhi, describes the life of the Indian leader as well as the history of India during Gandhi&#39;s time.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"Gandhi\", \"authors\": [\"Rajmohan Gandhi\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=FauJL7LKXmkC&dq=ghandi&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"Th