\"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1552854116\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781552854112\"}]}}, {\"id\": \"9L4NAAAAQAAJ\", \"etag\": \"jSEfpa1DZA4\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"buyLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ&rdid=book-9L4NAAAAQAAJ&rdot=1&source=gbs_api\", \"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": true, \"saleability\": \"FREE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/9L4NAAAAQAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": true, \"downloadLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/East_and_West_India_Sugar.pdf?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ&hl=&output=pdf&sig=ACfU3U0IRujbNz9wHXrgotwIQPdi14d-Tw&source=gbs_api\"}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false, \"downloadLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/East_and_West_India_Sugar.epub?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ&hl=&output=epub&source=gbs_api\"}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"ALL_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": true, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"FULL_PUBLIC_DOMAIN\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"A response to the pamphlet entitled &quot;Observations on the claims of the West-India colonists to a protecting duty on East-India sugar.&quot;\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"East and West India Sugar\", \"authors\": [\"Zachary Macaulay\"], \"infoLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"Or, A Refutation of the Claims of the West India Colonists to a Protecting Duty on East India Sugar\", \"pageCount\": 128, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"categories\": [\"Slavery\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"A response to the pamphlet entitled \\\"Observations on the claims of the West-India colonists to a protecting duty on East-India sugar.\\\"\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=india&hl=&cd=9&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": true}, \"publishedDate\": \"1823\", \"contentVersion\": \"0.1.4.0.full.1\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=9L4NAAAAQAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"OTHER\", \"identifier\": \"OXFORD:N10600930\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"6O62DwAAQBAJ\", \"etag\": \"djahzDENTTg\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"offers\": [{\"giftable\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 27990000}, \"retailPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 19990000}, \"finskyOfferType\": 1}], \"buyLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ&rdid=book-6O62DwAAQBAJ&rdot=1&source=gbs_api\", \"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"amount\": 27.99, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"retailPrice\": {\"amount\": 19.99, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"saleability\": \"FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/6O62DwAAQBAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": true, \"acsTokenLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/Fateful_Triangle-sample-pdf.acsm?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ&format=pdf&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api\"}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": true, \"acsTokenLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/Fateful_Triangle-sample-epub.acsm?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ&format=epub&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api\"}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"PARTIAL\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"SAMPLE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"Fateful Triangle expands our understanding of the diplomatic history of U.S.-India relations by highlighting the key role of the China factor, reassesses the origins and practice of Indian foreign policy and nonalignment, restores India ...\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"Fateful Triangle\", \"authors\": [\"Tanvi Madan\"], \"infoLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"How China Shaped U.S.-India Relations During the Cold War\", \"pageCount\": 397, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"Brookings Institution Press\", \"categories\": [\"Political Science\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"Taking a long view of the three-party relationship, and its future prospects In this Asian century, scholars, officials and journalists are increasingly focused on the fate of the rivalry between China and India. They see the U.S. relationships with the two Asian giants as now intertwined, after having followed separate paths during the Cold War. In Fateful Triangle, Tanvi Madan argues that China’s influence on the U.S.-India relationship is neither a recent nor a momentary phenomenon. Drawing on documents from India and the United States, she shows that American and Indian perceptions of and policy toward China significantly shaped U.S.-India relations in three crucial decades, from 1949 to 1979. Fateful Triangle updates our understanding of the diplomatic history of U.S.-India relations, highlighting China’s central role in it, reassesses the origins and practice of Indian foreign policy and nonalignment, and provides historical context for the interactions between the three countries. Madan’s assessment of this formative period in the triangular relationship is of more than historic interest. A key question today is whether the United States and India can, or should develop ever-closer ties as a way of countering China’s desire to be the dominant power in the broader Asian region. Fateful Triangle argues that history shows such a partnership is neither inevitable nor impossible. A desire to offset China brought the two countries closer together in the past, and could do so again. A look to history, however, also shows that shared perceptions of an external threat from China are necessary, but insufficient, to bring India and the United States into a close and sustained alignment: that requires agreement on the nature and urgency of the threat, as well as how to approach the threat strategically, economically, and ideologically. With its long view, Fateful Triangle offers insights for both present and future policymakers as they tackle a fateful, and evolving, triangle that has regional and global implications.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ&pg=PP1&dq=india&hl=&cd=10&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": true, \"image\": true}, \"publishedDate\": \"2020-02-04\", \"contentVersion\": \"1.2.2.0.preview.3\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": true, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=6O62DwAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9780815737728\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"0815737726\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}], \"tota