 \"pageCount\": 336, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"Penguin\", \"categories\": [\"Religion\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=67LmDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=67LmDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"This comprehensive, accessible, and authenticated guide to Islam is essential to understanding the world\'s fastest-growing religion. This essential guide to Islam covers every aspect of the Muslim faith and its history - from the life of the Prophet Muhammad and the teachings of the Koran to Islam in the 21st century. Celebrating the scientific, literary, and artistic achievements of the Islamic Golden Age and the ideas of philosophers and theologians across the centuries, it opens a window on the Islamic world. Clear factual writing offers insight into terms like Sharia law, the Caliphate, and jihad; Sunni and Shia divisions; and Sufi poetry and music. Images of Islamic art, architecture, calligraphy, and historical artefacts illustrate the articles while the Big Ideas\' trademark infographics and flowcharts explore and explain the central tenets of Islam, such as prayer, fasting, and pilgrimage. Modern issues such as fundamentalism are discussed in context alongside the work of peaceful traditionalists, modernizers, and women\'s rights campaigners, among others. Packed with inspiring quotations and bold illustrations, The Islam Book is an invaluable source of information both for members of one of the world\'s major religions and readers looking for a clear unbiased guide to the meaning of this faith.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=67LmDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=islam&hl=&cd=1&source=gbs_api\", \"ratingsCount\": 1, \"readingModes\": {\"text\": true, \"image\": true}, \"averageRating\": 4, \"publishedDate\": \"2020-08-04\", \"contentVersion\": \"1.4.4.0.preview.3\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": true, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=67LmDwAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9780744031041\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"0744031044\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"w3KYDwAAQBAJ\", \"etag\": \"lbi24oWBan4\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/w3KYDwAAQBAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"PARTIAL\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=w3KYDwAAQBAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"SAMPLE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"In What Is Islam?, Shahab Ahmed presents a bold new conceptualization of Islam that challenges dominant understandings grounded in the categories of &quot;religion&quot; and &quot;culture&quot; or those that privilege law and scripture.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"What Is Islam?\", \"authors\": [\"Shahab Ahmed\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=w3KYDwAAQBAJ&dq=islam&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"The Importance of Being Islamic\", \"pageCount\": 624, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"Princeton University Press\", \"categories\": [\"Religion\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=w3KYDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=w3KYDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"What is Islam? How do we grasp a human and historical phenomenon characterized by such variety and contradiction? What is \\\"Islamic\\\" about Islamic philosophy or Islamic art? Should we speak of Islam or of islams? Should we distinguish the Islamic (the religious) from the Islamicate (the cultural)? Or should we abandon \\\"Islamic\\\" altogether as an analytical term? In What Is Islam?, Shahab Ahmed presents a bold new conceptualization of Islam that challenges dominant understandings grounded in the categories of \\\"religion\\\" and \\\"culture\\\" or those that privilege law and scripture. He argues that these modes of thinking obstruct us from understanding Islam, distorting it, diminishing it, and rendering it incoherent. What Is Islam? formulates a new conceptual language for analyzing Islam. It presents a new paradigm of how Muslims have historically understood divine revelation—one that enables us to understand how and why Muslims through history have embraced values such as exploration, ambiguity, aestheticization, polyvalence, and relativism, as well as practices such as figural art, music, and even wine drinking as Islamic. It also puts forward a new understanding of the historical constitution of Islamic law and its relationship to philosophical ethics and political theory. A book that is certain to provoke debate and significantly alter our understanding of Islam, What Is Islam? reveals how Muslims have historically conceived of and lived with Islam as norms and truths that are at once contradictory yet coherent.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=w3KYDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=islam&hl=&cd=2&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": true}, \"publishedDate\": \"2017-10-31\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/What_Is_Islam.html?hl=&id=w3KYDwAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9780691178318\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"0691178313\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"fKW8wQEACAAJ\", \"etag\": \"JJTcfPocJcQ\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/fKW8wQEACAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": false, \"viewability\": \"NO_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=fKW8wQEACAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"NONE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"Encyclopaedia Britannica\", \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=fKW8wQEACAAJ&dq=islam&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"pageCount\": 1133, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"categories\": [\"Encyclopedias and dictionaries\"], \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=fKW8wQEACAAJ&dq=islam&hl=&cd=3&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"1973\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/Encyclopaedia_Britannica.html?hl=&id=fKW8wQEACAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"0852291736\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9780852291733\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"ScKIAAAAMAAJ\", \"etag\": \"KAqCjgPi7i0\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/ScKIAAAAMAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": false, \"viewability\": \"NO_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=ScKIAAAAMAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"NONE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"Professor al Faruqi&#39;s book is an invitation to the reader to attempt such an understanding. This volume seeks to portray the beliefs, practices, institutions, and history of Islam from the inside - as its adherents see them.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"Islam\", \"authors\": [\"Ismaʼil R. Al-Faruqi\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=ScKIAAAAMAAJ&dq=islam&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"pageCount\": 83, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"categories\": [\"Religion\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=ScKIAAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=ScKIAAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"The second half of the twentieth century has brought about a new awareness of Islam and Muslims to the inhabitants of Europe and North America. Due to our increased political, economic, and social contacts with Muslims, it is becoming ever more important - nay, crucial - for us to understand the religion and culture of Islam. Such an understanding is not easy, author Ismail R. al Faruqi points out, for Western thinking is clouded by prejudices about Islam, its culture, and its adherents. It is time to launch a new effort that will seek to bridge the gulf separating westerners and Muslims. Professor al Faruqi\'s book is an invitation to the reader to attempt such an understanding. This volume seeks to portray the beliefs, practices, institutions, and history of Islam from the inside - as its adherents see them. The seven chapters explore these subjects: (1) who are the Muslims and what are their basic beliefs; (2) the five pillars, or basic tenets, of Islam; (3) the prophethood of Muhammad and major Muslim celebrations; (4,5,6) the social, economic, and political ideals and institutions of Islam; and (7) the effect of Islamic beliefs on artistic expression and an overview of Islamic history.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=ScKIAAAAMAAJ&q=islam&dq=islam&hl=&cd=4&source=gbs_api\", \"ratingsCount\": 1, \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"averageRating\": 2, \"publishedDate\": \"1995\", \"contentVersion\": \"0.2.3.0.preview.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/Islam.html?hl=&id=ScKIAAAAMAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"OTHER\", \"identifier\": \"IND:30000045605213\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"v21NCwAAQBAJ\", \"etag\": \"dKwqXtLvuqM\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"offers\": [{\"giftable\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 19990000}, \"retailPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 19990000}, \"finskyOfferType\": 1}], \"buyLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=v21NCwAAQBAJ&rdid=book-v21NCwAAQBAJ&rdot=1&source=gbs_api\", \"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"amount\": 19.99, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"retailPrice\": {\"amount\": 19.99, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"saleability\": \"FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/v21NCwAAQBAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": true, \"acsTokenLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/The_Lawful_and_the_Prohibited_in_Islam_A-sample-pdf.acsm?id=v21NCwAAQBAJ&format=pdf&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api\"}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"PARTIAL\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=v21NCwAAQBAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"SAMPLE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"Over the years since ite first publication in 1960, this volume has enjoyed a huge readership in the Arabic speaking world and is now in its 20th edition.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"The Lawful and the Prohibited in Islam (Al-Halal Wal Haram Fil Islam)\", \"authors\": [\"Yusuf Al-Qaradawi\"], \"infoLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=v21NCwAAQBAJ&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"pageCount\": 368, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"American Trust Publications\", \"categories\": [\"Religion\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=v21NCwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=v21NCwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"The Lawful and the Prohibited in Islam is a long-awaited translation of Dr. Yusuf Al-Qaradawi\'s well-known Arabic work, Al-Halal Al-Haram Fil-Islam. Over the years since ite first publication in 1960, this volume has enjoyed a huge readership in the Arabic speaking world and is now in its 20th edition. It came to dispel the ambiguities surrounding the honorable Shari\'ah, and to fulfill the essential needs of the Muslims in this age. It clarifies the Halal (Lawful) and why it is Halal, and the Haram (Prohibited) and why it is Haram, referring to the Book of Allah and the Sunnah of His Messenger (peace be on him). It answers all the questions which may face the Muslims today, and refutes the ambiguities and lies about Islam. In a very simple way, Al-Halal Al-Haram Fil-Islam delves into the authentic references in Islamic jurisprudence and fiqh. It therefrom extracts judgments of interest to contemporary Muslims in the areas of worship, business dealings, marriage and divorce, food and drink, dress and ornaments, patterns of behavior, individual and group relations, family and social ethics, habits and social customs. Referring to authentic texts, it clarifies that \\\"Permission is the rule in everything, unless it is otherwise specified in matters that adversely affect individuals or groups.\\\" It also clarifies that \\\"Allah is the only authority who has the right to legislate for the lawful and the prohibited.\\\"\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=v21NCwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=islam&hl=&cd=5&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": true}, \"publishedDate\": \"1999-01-30\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": true, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=v21NCwAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9780892590162\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"0892590165\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"n1BFCQAAQBAJ\", \"etag\": \"w+ZCVzwQz2A\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"offers\": [{\"giftable\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 27950000}, \"retailPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 15370000}, \"finskyOfferType\": 1}], \"buyLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=n1BFCQAAQBAJ&rdid=book-n1BFCQAAQBAJ&rdot=1&source=gbs_api\", \"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"amount\": 27.95, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"retailPrice\": {\