nt?id=hqQrzgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"The hunt begins! As the Predators make their Marvel debut, experience their original comics legacy! Nowhere is safe when the remorseless alien killers stalk the concrete jungle of New York City, leave a trail of death across the American Southwest and ignite the Cold War in Siberia! And did Predators come to Earth during Vietnam and World War I? The hunters make a new enemy in Dutch\'s brother Detective Schaefer! Predator takes on psychotic Predator in the Pine Barrens of New Jersey! And in 1950s Hollywood, only a child with special glasses can see the monster in the midst of Tinseltown! It\'s total carnage, Predator-style! COLLECTING: Predator (1989) 1-4, Predator 2 (1991) 1-2, Predator: Big Game (1991) 1-4, Predator: Cold War (1991) 1-4, Predator: The Bloody Sands of Time (1992) 1-2, Predator: Bad Blood (1993) 1-4, Predator: Invaders from the Fourth Dimension (1994) 1, Predator: Dark River (1996) 1-4, Predator: Strange Roux (1996) 1, Predator: Kindred (1996) 1-4; material from Dark Horse Presents (1986) 46, 119; Dark Horse Comics (1992) 1-2, 4-7, 10-14, 16-18, 20-21; A Decade of Dark Horse (1996) 1\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=hqQrzgEACAAJ&dq=predator&hl=&cd=3&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"2021-08-03\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/Predator_the_Original_Years_Omnibus_Vol.html?hl=&id=hqQrzgEACAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1302928961\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781302928964\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"9PNOEAAAQBAJ\", \"etag\": \"+PdRoj5p5kI\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"i