 soon decapitated human bodies are littering the surrounding area. The Russian authorities are baffled, but deep within the Pentagon, someone knows that the Predators are back. BIG GAME Deep in the rugged New Mexico desert, a strange aircraft has landed: an alien Predator has arrived, hunting for human prey. For Corporal Enoch Nakai, a Navajo soldier, it is a legend come back to life: the return of the horned monster who was destroyed by the hero Nayenezgani, the mythical monster slayer. Using the wisdom of his ancestors, Nakai will confront the Predator in a final battle worthy of legend. But this time, will the hero emerge the victor?\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=9PNOEAAAQBAJ&dq=predator&hl=&cd=4&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": true, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"2018-01-30\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/The_Complete_Predator_Omnibus.html?hl=&id=9PNOEAAAQBAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781785653421\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1785653423\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"ZXIxzgEACAAJ\", \"etag\": \"ZtwMOmqkqUs\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/ZXIxzgEACAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": false, \"viewability\": \"NO_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=ZXIxzgEACAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"NONE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"And despite their animosity, only they can fight it down. The Predator is an enemies-to-lovers, dark, contemporary romance set in a fictional universe with mafia, passion and incredible storytelling.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"The Predator\", \"authors\": [\"RuNyx\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=ZXIxzgEACAAJ&dq=predator&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"A Dark Contemporary Mafia Romance\", \"pageCount\": 318, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=ZXIxzgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=ZXIxzgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"What happens when an unstoppable force meets an immovable object in the field of death? In the dark underbelly of the mob, Tristan Caine has been an anomaly. As the only non-blooded member in the high circle of the Tenebrae Outfit, he is an enigma to all - his skills unparalleled, his morality questionable, and his motives unknown. He is lethal and he knows it. As does Morana Vitalio, the genius extraordinaire daughter of the rival family. What Caine does with weapons, Morana does with computers. When a twenty-year old mystery resurfaces, Morana infiltrates Caine\'s house, intent on killing him, unaware of a tie that binds them together. Hate, heat, and history clash together with unexpected sparks. But something bigger, something worse is happening in their world. And despite their animosity, only they can fight it down. The Predator is an enemies-to-lovers, dark, contemporary romance set in a fictional universe with mafia, passion and incredible storytelling.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=ZXIxzgEACAAJ&dq=predator&hl=&cd=5&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"2020-12\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRat