s_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=tRq2AAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api\"}, \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=tRq2AAAACAAJ&dq=ufos&hl=&cd=3&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"1996-01-01\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/UFOs_Over_Africa.html?hl=&id=tRq2AAAACAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1881852156\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781881852155\"}]}}, {\"id\": \"XjxELQAACAAJ\", \"etag\": \"6YKtR/x8ItI\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/XjxELQAACAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": false, \"viewability\": \"NO_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=XjxELQAACAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"NONE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"It&#39;s been said that famous blackouts, abductions, and special visitations have all occurred while normal New Yorkers have lead their daily lives. So search the skies with us in this comprehensive history of UFOs Over New York. If you dare.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"UFOs Over New York\", \"authors\": [\"Preston Dennett\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=XjxELQAACAAJ&dq=ufos&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"A True History of Extraterrestrial Encounters in the Empire State\", \"pageCount\": 256, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"Schiffer Pub Limited\", \"categories\": [\"Body, Mind & Spirit\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=XjxELQAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=XjxELQAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"New York State is one of the most famous and influential places on the planet, so it should come as no surprise that it has a rich UFO history. The state\'s first UFO sighting came more than 150 years ago, but it doesn\'t end there! From important government military intelligence and commercial airline reports to downtown NYC sightings of flying saucers on Broadway and at the Empire State Building, UFOs have been witnessed in the New York State skyscape by some of the most credible people in history. Police officers, movie stars, business men and women, and others have all been privy to strange UFO encounters. Whether it\'s Jimi Hendrix saved by aliens in upstate New York or geologists investigating crop circles on the north shore of Oneida Lake, people are stepping up to tell their stories. It\'s been said that famous blackouts, abductions, and special visitations have all occurred while normal New Yorkers have lead their daily lives. So search the skies with us in this comprehensive history of UFOs Over New York. If you dare.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=XjxELQAACAAJ&dq=ufos&hl=&cd=4&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"2008\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/UFOs_Over_New_York.html?hl=&id=XjxELQAACAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"076432974X\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9780764329746\"}]}}, {\"id\": \"IaA8mZqhjPkC\", \"etag\": \"CkHfnzMkonI\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"offers\": [{\"giftable\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 11990000}, \"retailPrice\": {\"currencyCode\": \"USD\", \"amountInMicros\": 11990000}, \"finskyOfferType\": 1}], \"buyLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=IaA8mZqhjPkC&rdid=book-IaA8mZqhjPkC&rdot=1&source=gbs_api\", \"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": true, \"listPrice\": {\"amount\": 11.99, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"retailPrice\": {\"amount\": 11.99, \"currencyCode\": \"USD\"}, \"saleability\": \"FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/IaA8mZqhjPkC\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": true, \"acsTokenLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books/download/UFOs-sample-epub.acsm?id=IaA8mZqhjPkC&format=epub&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api\"}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": true, \"viewability\": \"PARTIAL\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=IaA8mZqhjPkC&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"SAMPLE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"UFOs is at once a complete account of Alexander&#39;s findings, and a call to action. There are no conspiracy theories here—only hard facts—but they are merely the beginning.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"UFOs\", \"authors\": [\"John B. Alexander, Ph.D.\"], \"infoLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=IaA8mZqhjPkC&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"Myths, Conspiracies, and Realities\", \"pageCount\": 336, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"Macmillan\", \"categories\": [\"Science\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=IaA8mZqhjPkC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=IaA8mZqhjPkC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"Foreword by Jacques F. Vallee Introduction by Burt Rutan Commentary by Tom Clancy A never-before-heard firsthand account of a government insider\'s experience on the cutting edge of UFO exploration While still on active duty in the U.S. Army during the 1980s, Colonel John B. Alexander, Ph.D., created an interagency group to explore the controversial topic of UFOs. Participants came from the Army, Navy, Air Force, CIA, NSA, DIA, and the aerospace industry. All members held Top Secret clearance. What they discovered was not at all what was expected. UFOs covers the numerous cases they saw, and answers questions like: • What was really in Hanger 18? • Did a UFO land at Holloman Air Force Base? • What happened at Roswell? • What is Majestic 12? • What is the Aviary? • What does the government know about UFOs? • What has happened with disclosure in other countries? • Has the U.S. reverse engineered a UFO? • Why don\'t presidents get access to UFO info? UFOs is at once a complete account of Alexander\'s findings, and a call to action. There are no conspiracy theories here—only hard facts—but they are merely the beginning. Serious research is needed in order to understand and anticipate the workings of UFOs, and John Alexander is leading the charge.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=IaA8mZqhjPkC&printsec=frontcover&dq=ufos&hl=&cd=5&source=gbs_api\", \"ratingsCount\": 1, \"readingModes\": {\"text\": true, \"image\": false}, \"averageRating\": 2, \"publishedDate\": \"2011-02-15\", \"contentVersion\": \"0.6.8.0.preview.2\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": true, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=IaA8mZqhjPkC\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781429994835\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1429994835\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": f