the scientific establishment takes a dim view of UFOs and abduction evidence and examines how the US government has collected and suppressed UFO evidence. UFOs, ETs, and Alien Abductions is a wide-ranging examination of all things off-planet that falls into 3 sections. 1. UFOs: evidence and belief between 1947 through 1965 and Cold War mysteries 2. The changing nature of UFO phenomenon from 1965 to the present, which makes the case for the existence of humanoid crew members seen in and around landed UFOs. This section also examines six well-documented abduction cases, and includes the author detailing his own research involvement with the evidence. He refutes the belief that all abductees are mentally disturbed and that a psychological disturbance explains the experience. 3. The third section is devoted to a very meaty and controversial analysis of science, politics, and UFOs.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=bietkYXJjJsC&printsec=frontcover&dq=ufos&hl=&cd=6&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": true}, \"publishedDate\": \"2013-06-01\", \"contentVersion\": \"0.1.0.0.preview.1\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/UFOs_ETs_and_Alien_Abductions.html?hl=&id=bietkYXJjJsC\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781571746955\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"1571746951\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"UD5-AAAAMAAJ\", \"etag\": \"2BNOxUziVcI\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/UD5-AAAAMAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": false, \"viewability\": \"NO_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=UD5-AAAAMAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"NONE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"A surprising collection of writings on the subject of UFOs and alien abduction challenges serious scientists to explore this field, presenting the various recurring themes and unsoved puzzles surrounding our fascination with these ...\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"UFOs and Abductions\", \"authors\": [\"David Michael Jacobs\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=UD5-AAAAMAAJ&dq=ufos&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"Challenging the Borders of Knowledge\", \"pageCount\": 382, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"categories\": [\"Body, Mind & Spirit\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=UD5-AAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=UD5-AAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"A surprising collection of writings on the subject of UFOs and alien abduction challenges serious scientists to explore this field, presenting the various recurring themes and unsoved puzzles surrounding our fascination with these unexplained phenomena.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=UD5-AAAAMAAJ&q=ufos&dq=ufos&hl=&cd=7&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"2000\", \"contentVersion\": \"0.1.1.0.preview.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/UFOs_and_Abductions.html?hl=&id=UD5-AAAAMAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"OTHER\", \"identifier\": \"UOM:39015050326746\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"uuGjoAEACAAJ\", \"etag\": \"OBX8BYDEtxk\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/uuGjoAEACAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": false, \"viewability\": \"NO_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=uuGjoAEACAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"NONE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"This is the new must-have UFO book. For beginners and experienced researchers alike, historian Richard Dolan covers the full range of this incredibly complex topic in his uniquely engaging style.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"UFOs for the 21st Century Mind\", \"authors\": [\"Richard M. Dolan\", \"George Noory\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=uuGjoAEACAAJ&dq=ufos&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"A Fresh Guide to an Ancient Mystery\", \"pageCount\": 486, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"CreateSpace\", \"categories\": [\"Body, Mind & Spirit\"], \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=uuGjoAEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=uuGjoAEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"This is the new must-have UFO book. For beginners and experienced researchers alike, historian Richard Dolan covers the full range of this incredibly complex topic in his uniquely engaging style. He offers fresh insights on everything connected to UFOs: ancient aliens, modern encounters, abductions, channelers, the politics and cover-up, the black budget world, the bizarre science, the social dimensions (read YouTube and Facebook), the future, and much more. Toward that end, Dolan gives practical insights on how to distinguish and investigate UFOs in today\'s world, where we are flooded with claims and videos and data of all types. In addition, as one of ufology\'s pioneers in the deep analysis of the cover-up, he offers an original perspective on how it all works and why the cover-up, despite being so entrenched and insidious, is nevertheless bound to end. He also writes on the nature of contact, speculating on who these \\\"Others\\\" might be. Finally, Dolan takes the reader through the \\\"weird science\\\" of UFOs, covering everything from propulsion to spacetime to consciousness and more. UFOs for the 21st Century Mind is a roadmap pointing the way forward in a field filled with uncertainty and obfuscation. In so doing, it is set to reposition an ancient phenomenon into a contemporary state of mind, reminding you just why the greatest mystery of our time is also one of the most important. Contents: Introduction 1. What Are UFOs? 2. Theories of Ancient Visitation 3. Into Modernity: Airships, Foo Fighters, and Flying Saucers, 1896 to 1969 4. UFO Secrecy and Those Who Fought It 5. Digging Deeper-The Breakaway Civilization 6. High Strangeness-UFOs from 1970 to 1990 7. UFOs, 1991 to the Present 8. Contact and Abduction 9. The Growth of Ufology 10. Who Are They? What Do They Want? 11. Weird Science: Propulsion, Energy, Spacetime, and Consciousness 12. Into the Future, Into Ourselves Conclusion 486 p. Illustrated Endorsements: \\\"In a field that can be so confusing, so complex, Richard Dolan has taken his many years of thinking about UFOs and written a completely fresh overview of the entire subject. . . . This is an ambitious work that truly ties the many different aspects of the subject together. It\'s rare to find something like this, especially considering the care and thoroughness that went into it.\\\" -- George Noory, host of Coast to Coast AM. \\\"As a follow-up to his previous books exploring the relationship between UFOs and the National Security State, historian Richard Dolan widens his perspective to explore all aspects of this provocative phenomenon. In this role, he takes us on a journey that brings to life the subtlety and depth of this rich subject, a truly captivating read.\\\" --H. E. Puthoff, Ph.D., Director, Institute for Advanced Studies at Austin \\\"UFOs For the 21st Century Mind represents a new kind of book - one that clearly and intelligently addresses literally every aspect and implication of the most maligned, misunderstood and compelling subject in human history. Richard Dolan\'s newest work is perfect reading for serious students of ufology as well as the absolute beginner. Inspired, particularly well written, and the product of a first class mind for this or any other century.\\\" --Peter Robbins, coauthor of the U.K. bestseller, Left At East Gate: A First-Hand Account of the Rendlesham Forest UFO Incident, Its Cover-up and Investigation \\\"This is an invaluable treatment of the known facets and seemingly endless implications regarding UFOs, with a much-appreciated focus on the human experience. A job well done, Richard.\\\" -- Sam Maranto, Investigative Researcher\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=uuGjoAEACAAJ&dq=ufos&hl=&cd=8&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"2014-01-21\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/UFOs_for_the_21st_Century_Mind.html?hl=&id=uuGjoAEACAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_10\", \"identifier\": \"149529160X\"}, {\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9781495291609\"}]}}, {\"id\": \"QzBWzgEACAAJ\", \"etag\": \"ygKDMCp7ChA\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/QzBWzgEACAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": false, \"viewability\": \"NO_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=QzBWzgEACAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"NONE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"This is one of the most important books ever written on the clandestine world of the UFO cover-up. Grant Cameron and Scott Crain do more than demonstrate the reality of an extraterrestrial presence on Earth.\"}, \"volumeInfo\": {\"title\": \"UFOs, Area 51, and Government Informants\", \"authors\": [\"Scott Crain, Jr\", \"Grant Cameron\"], \"infoLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=QzBWzgEACAAJ&dq=ufos&hl=&source=gbs_api\", \"language\": \"en\", \"subtitle\": \"A Report on Government Involvement in UFO Crash Retrievals\", \"pageCount\": 342, \"printType\": \"BOOK\", \"publisher\": \"Independently Published\", \"imageLinks\": {\"thumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=QzBWzgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api\", \"smallThumbnail\": \"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=QzBWzgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api\"}, \"description\": \"This is one of the most important books ever written on the clandestine world of the UFO cover-up. Grant Cameron and Scott Crain do more than demonstrate the reality of an extraterrestrial presence on Earth. Through tenacious investigation and impeccable research, they shine a light into the CIA, NSA, Air Force, Navy, and other inside groups that have managed this secret for decades. Their conclusion is inescapable and shocking: this is a secret that the insiders themselves struggle to understand and contain. \\\"Government agencies, at various times, perceive a need to release some UFO information to the public. Some, definitely not all. How do they do it? Always via avenues that leave no one at risk. That means ensuring there is no direct connection between the agency and whomever is doing the actual releasing. It also means the necessity of mixing in some false information. It means, ultimately, to tell the truth, but tell it with a slant. Until there is a full disclosure of the UFO/ET reality, deniability will remain paramount to those in possession of this great secret.\\\" - By the authors, from the book\'s Introduction.\", \"previewLink\": \"http://books.google.com/books?id=QzBWzgEACAAJ&dq=ufos&hl=&cd=9&source=gbs_api\", \"readingModes\": {\"text\": false, \"image\": false}, \"publishedDate\": \"2020-10-30\", \"contentVersion\": \"preview-1.0.0\", \"maturityRating\": \"NOT_MATURE\", \"allowAnonLogging\": false, \"canonicalVolumeLink\": \"https://books.google.com/books/about/UFOs_Area_51_and_Government_Informants.html?hl=&id=QzBWzgEACAAJ\", \"industryIdentifiers\": [{\"type\": \"ISBN_13\", \"identifier\": \"9798556079717\"}], \"panelizationSummary\": {\"containsEpubBubbles\": false, \"containsImageBubbles\": false}}}, {\"id\": \"D4YaAAAACAAJ\", \"etag\": \"F9MZ/r67dAM\", \"kind\": \"books#volume\", \"saleInfo\": {\"country\": \"US\", \"isEbook\": false, \"saleability\": \"NOT_FOR_SALE\"}, \"selfLink\": \"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/D4YaAAAACAAJ\", \"accessInfo\": {\"pdf\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"epub\": {\"isAvailable\": false}, \"country\": \"US\", \"embeddable\": false, \"viewability\": \"NO_PAGES\", \"publicDomain\": false, \"webReaderLink\": \"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=D4YaAAAACAAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api\", \"accessViewStatus\": \"NONE\", \"quoteSharingAllowed\": false, \"textToSpeechPermission\": \"ALLOWED\"}, \"searchInfo\": {\"textSnippet\": \"From over 5000 reported California UFO encounters, here there are early accounts of Native American UFO encounters, the 1896 California